      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *    XIJICOMM INTERFACE
       01  XIJICOMM-CA.
           COPY  XIJICOMM.
      *   처리DC  INTERFACE
       01  XDJL4073-CA.
           COPY  XDJL4073.
      *   출력영역확보　및　초기화INTERFACE
       01  XZUGOTMY-CA.
           COPY  XZUGOTMY.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       LINKAGE                         SECTION.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *    COMMON AREA
       01  YCCOMMON-CA.
           COPY  YCCOMMON.
      *    AS COPYBOOK
       01  YNJL4073-CA.
           COPY  YNJL4073.
      *    AS COPYBOOK
       01  YPJL4073-CA.
           COPY  YPJL4073.
      *=================================================================
       PROCEDURE                       DIVISION
                                       USING       YCCOMMON-CA
                                                   YNJL4073-CA
                                                   .
      *=================================================================
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@  처리메인
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S0000-MAIN-RTN.

      *@  초기화
           PERFORM S1000-INITIALIZE-RTN
              THRU S1000-INITIALIZE-EXT

      *@  입력값　CHECK
           PERFORM S2000-VALIDATION-RTN
              THRU S2000-VALIDATION-EXT

      *@  업무처리
           PERFORM S3000-PROCESS-RTN
              THRU S3000-PROCESS-EXT

      *@  처리종료
           PERFORM S9000-FINAL-RTN
              THRU S9000-FINAL-EXT
           .
       S0000-MAIN-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@  초기화
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S1000-INITIALIZE-RTN.
      *@1 초기화

      *@1.1 출력영역확보 파라미터 및 결과코드 초기화
           INITIALIZE    WK-AREA
                         XIJICOMM-IN
                         XZUGOTMY-IN

      *@1.2 출력영역 확보
           #GETOUT       YPJL4073-CA

      *@1.3 COMMON AREA SETTING 공통IC프로그램 호출
           #DYCALL IJICOMM YCCOMMON-CA XIJICOMM-CA

      *@1.4 호출결과 확인
           IF COND-XIJICOMM-OK
              CONTINUE
           ELSE
              #ERROR XIJICOMM-R-ERRCD
                     XIJICOMM-R-TREAT-CD
                     XIJICOMM-R-STAT
           END-IF
           .
       S1000-INITIALIZE-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@  입력값검증
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S2000-VALIDATION-RTN.
      *@2 입력값검증

      *@2.1 처리구분CHECK
      *@처리내용:처리구분 "01" 아닐경우 오류처리한다
           IF YNJL4073-PRCSS-DSTIC NOT = CO-CHA-01
              #ERROR CO-B3000070 CO-UKJL0036 CO-STAT-ERROR
           END-IF
           .
       S2000-VALIDATION-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@  업무처리
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3000-PROCESS-RTN.
      *@3 업무처리

      *@3.1 DC호출
           PERFORM S3100-DJL4073-CALL-RTN
              THRU S3100-DJL4073-CALL-EXT
           .
       S3000-PROCESS-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@   DC호출
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3100-DJL4073-CALL-RTN.
      *@1 포괄신용공여한도설정대상

      *@3.1.1 입력파라미터 조립
           INITIALIZE    XDJL4073-IN

      *    처리구분
           MOVE YNJL4073-PRCSS-DSTIC
             TO XDJL4073-I-PRCSS-DSTIC
      *    기준년월일
           MOVE YNJL4073-BASE-YMD
             TO XDJL4073-I-BASE-YMD
191220*    관리부점코드
           MOVE YNJL4073-MGT-BRNCD
             TO XDJL4073-I-MGT-BRNCD

      *@3.1.2 프로그램 호출
      *@처리내용:DC프로그램호출
           #DYCALL DJL4073 YCCOMMON-CA XDJL4073-CA

      *@3.1.3 처리결과CHECK
      *@처리내용:리턴코드가 정상(00) 아닐경우 오류처리한다
           EVALUATE TRUE
           WHEN COND-XDJL4073-OK
      *@      출력처리
               PERFORM S6000-OUTPUT-RTN
                  THRU S6000-OUTPUT-EXT
           WHEN COND-XDJL4073-NOTFOUND
               MOVE 'N0000002'
                 TO WK-MESSAGE
           WHEN OTHER
               #ERROR XDJL4073-R-ERRCD
                      XDJL4073-R-TREAT-CD
                      XDJL4073-R-STAT
           END-EVALUATE
           .

       S3100-DJL4073-CALL-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@  출력처리
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S6000-OUTPUT-RTN.
      *@4 출력처리

      *@4.1 출력라인수 조립
           MOVE XDJL4073-O-OUTPT-LINE-CNT1
             TO YPJL4073-OUTPT-LINE-CNT1

      *@4.2 그리드1 조립
           PERFORM VARYING WK-I FROM 1 BY 1
                   UNTIL   WK-I > YPJL4073-OUTPT-LINE-CNT1
      *       기준년월일
               MOVE XDJL4073-O-BASE-YMD(WK-I)
                 TO YPJL4073-BASE-YMD(WK-I)
      *       관리부점코드
               MOVE XDJL4073-O-MGT-BRNCD(WK-I)
                 TO YPJL4073-MGT-BRNCD(WK-I)
      *       부점명
               MOVE XDJL4073-O-BRN-NAME(WK-I)
                 TO YPJL4073-BRN-NAME(WK-I)
      *       대분류업종코드
               MOVE XDJL4073-O-LAG-CLSFI-BZTYP-CD(WK-I)
                 TO YPJL4073-LAG-CLSFI-BZTYP-CD(WK-I)
      *       대분류업종코드명
               MOVE XDJL4073-O-LAG-C-BZTYP-CD-NAME(WK-I)
                 TO YPJL4073-LAG-C-BZTYP-CD-NAME(WK-I)
      *       산업별TE
               MOVE XDJL4073-O-IDSTRY-PER-TE-AMT(WK-I)
                 TO YPJL4073-IDSTRY-PER-TE-AMT(WK-I)
      *       비중
               MOVE XDJL4073-O-WGHTZ(WK-I)
                 TO YPJL4073-WGHTZ(WK-I)
      *       편중관리익스포져금액
               MOVE XDJL4073-O-LNUP-MGT-EXPSR-AMT(WK-I)
                 TO YPJL4073-LNUP-MGT-EXPSR-AMT(WK-I)
      *       투자비중
               MOVE XDJL4073-O-INVST-WGHT(WK-I)
                 TO YPJL4073-INVST-WGHT(WK-I)
      *       편중관리대상여부
               MOVE XDJL4073-O-LNUP-MGT-TAGET-YN(WK-I)
                 TO YPJL4073-LNUP-MGT-TAGET-YN(WK-I)
      *       편중관리비율
               MOVE XDJL4073-O-LNUP-MGT-CST-RT(WK-I)
                 TO YPJL4073-LNUP-MGT-CST-RT(WK-I)
      *       관리비중초과여부
               MOVE XDJL4073-O-MGT-WGHT-EXCS-YN(WK-I)
                 TO YPJL4073-MGT-WGHT-EXCS-YN(WK-I)
      *       여유액
               MOVE XDJL4073-O-SEXTR-AMT(WK-I)
                 TO YPJL4073-SEXTR-AMT(WK-I)
           END-PERFORM
           .
       S6000-OUTPUT-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@  처리종료
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S9000-FINAL-RTN.
      *@5 종료처리

      *@5.1 폼ID SET
      *@처리내용:화면폼ID SET
           #BOFMID 'V1KJL04073000'

      *@5.2 프로그램 종료
      *@처리내용:프로그램 정상종료
           #OKEXIT CO-STAT-OK WK-MESSAGE
           .
       S9000-FINAL-EXT.
           EXIT.
